pokedexEntries.red: Adores circular objects. Wanders the streets on a nightly basis to look for dropped loose change.
pokedexEntries.blue: Adores circular objects. Wanders the streets on a nightly basis to look for dropped loose change.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Appears to be more active at night. It loves round and shiny things. It can't stop from picking them up.
pokedexEntries.gold: It is fascinated by round objects. It can't stop playing with them until it tires and falls asleep.
pokedexEntries.silver: It loves anything that shines. It especially adores coins that it picks up and secretly hoards.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It loves things that sparkle. When it sees a shiny object, the gold coin on its head shines too.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Meowth withdraw their sharp claws into their paws to silently sneak about. For some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: All it does is sleep during the daytime. At night, it patrols its territory with its eyes aglow.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Adores round objects. It wanders the streets on a nightly basis to look for dropped loose change.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly.

pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.
pokedexEntries.sun: It lies around all day, becoming active near dusk. At night, it wanders the city in search of loose change.
pokedexEntries.moon: It loves shiny things. It often fights with Murkrow over prey they're both trying to catch.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: When visiting a junkyard, you may catch sight of it having an intense fight with Murkrow over shiny objects.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: It loves coins, so if you give it one, you can make friends with Meowth easily. But it’s fickle, so you can’t count on that friendship lasting.
